message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper deals with conversational question answering, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also uses BERT, a popular NLP technique, which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves attention mechanisms and multi-task learning, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with improving the performance of ConvQA, which can be seen as a problem in neural networks (cs.NE).
